title: Jennifer Lopez Posts Cryptic Instagram Message About 'Timing' as Drake Hangs With Donald Glover
text: Jennifer Lopez Posts Cryptic Instagram Message About 'Timing' as Drake Hangs With Donald Glover by Jennifer Drysdale 4:10 PM   Photo: Instagram What's going on here, J.Lo? Jennifer Lopez took to Instagram on Saturday to share a cryptic message about timing -- as her rumored beau, Drake, spent some time with some "very inspiring humans." The 30-year-old rapper, meanwhile, spent his Saturday hanging out with some pals -- including Donald Glover. "Very Inspiring Humans," he wrote alongside the black-and-white photo. A photo posted by champagnepapi (@champagnepapi) on Feb 3, 2017 at 4:17pm PST A photo posted by Jennifer Lopez (@jlo) on Feb 5, 2017 at 1:37pm PST A video posted by Jennifer Lopez (@jlo) on Feb 5, 2017 at 1:02am PST A video posted by Jennifer Lopez (@jlo) on Feb 5, 2017 at 1:04am PST Though Lopez and Drake spent their weekend apart, something tells us the two were on each other's minds -- and it might have something to do with the sexy snap the mother of two shared on Friday. Lopez wasn't afraid to flaunt her bangin' body -- underboob and all -- in a seriously racy shot. See more in the video below.
